Castlevania 2 Deadly Curse Randomizer
Version:    1
Date:       October 26, 2017
URL:
    https://abyssonym.wordpress.com/2017/10/27/castlevania-2-deadly-curse/
Contact:    https://twitter.com/abyssonym

--- HOW TO USE ---
Running the randomizer:
    Windows users may use the executable file, "cv2_deadly_curse.exe". Other users, please run "randomizer.py" using Python version 2.7.

Source rom file:
    This randomizer requires a Castlevania 2: Simon's Quest rom with the following hash:
    MD5 - 1b827c602c904d8c846499c9f54b93e0 (NA)

Seed value:
    Input a seed value here, or leave it blank if you don't care.

Flags:
    i  Randomize items.
    m  Randomize monsters.
    o  Randomize mansion order.

Output files:
    The randomizer will output a new, randomized rom with the seed in the filename.

SPECIAL THANKS:
    DSF AKA DoodSF AKA deranged_squirrel_fighter, who commissioned this randomizer. It's thanks to him that everyone can play CV2 randomized now. Check out his Twitch channel at https://www.twitch.tv/doodsf where he plays tons of randomizers.
    Also thanks to tkempkes on romhacking.net for his CV2 Annoyance Fixes.

